Ruby/GtkGLExt
=============
Ruby/GtkGLExt is a Ruby binding of GtkGLExt.

Requirements
------------
   Ruby: http://www.ruby-lang.org/ (1.8.0 and 1.6.8 should work fine)
   GTK+: http://www.gtk.org/
   GtkGLExt: http://gtkglext.sourceforge.net/
   OpenGL: see http://www.opengl.org/users/downloads/
   rbogl, the Ruby OpenGL binding: http://www2.giganet.net/~yoshi/ (see README.rbogl)
   Ruby/GLib2, Ruby/GTK2: http://ruby-gnome2.sourceforge.jp/

Install
-------
   0. install ruby, GTK+, GtkGLExt, rbogl, Ruby/GLib2 and Ruby/GTK2
   1. ruby extconf.rb
   2. make
   3. su
   4. make install

